OL,3,CPensions Minister ordered to repay
OL,4,C#1,367 after expenses breach
OL,6,FBut Mr Maynard was cleared of
OL,7,Fwrongdoing over his "higher than
OL,8,Faverage" claim of #106,000 for
OL,9,Fprinting and related costs since 2010,
OL,10,Fwith the watchdog saying a
OL,11,F"comprehensive audit" of the relevant
OL,12,Fperiod was not undertaken due to
OL,13,F"resource constraints".
OL,15,FThe junior minister previously told
OL,16,Fthe Sunday Times, which broke the
OL,17,Fstory, that he believed he had the
OL,18,Fproper arrangements in place but would
OL,19,Fabide by any IPSA findings.
