OL,6,FA report by IPSA's compliance officer
OL,7,Fpublished on Thursday said: "The MP
OL,8,Freasonably believed he had put in
OL,9,Fplace an agreement with IPSA to allow
OL,10,Ffor the occasional use of his
OL,11,Fconstituency office for non-
OL,12,Fparliamentary purposes and made
OL,13,Fregular payments to Ipsa for this
OL,14,Fpurpose," the report said.
