OL,6,FIt added: "On the assumption, the
OL,7,F'Riso' (printer) has been used 10% of
OL,8,Fthe time for non-parliamentary
OL,9,Fpurposes it would appropriate for the
OL,10,FMP to reimburse Ipsa the sum of
OL,11,F#1,257.28.
OL,13,F"In recognition of the possibility of
OL,14,Finaccurately logged usage of the
OL,15,Fconstituency office for party-
OL,16,Fpolitical activity, the MP has also
OL,17,Fagreed to an additional repayment of
OL,18,F#110."
