OL,6,FMr Maynard said he had paid back the
OL,7,Frecommended sum and welcomed the
OL,8,Ffindings of the report, which he said
OL,9,F"makes no direct criticism of me or of
OL,10,Fmy office".
OL,12,F"I am grateful to the compliance
OL,13,Fofficer for his time in considering
OL,14,Fthis matter," the MP said.
OL,16,F"I welcome his report, which makes no
OL,17,Fdirect criticism of me or of my
OL,18,Foffice, and accept the findings.
